{"tid":1362250,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"建議727 元朗商店 / 圍村放Memo 紙係門囗","createTime":"2019-07-24T22:49:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T22:51:14.000Z","uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5bab7e81f8a122e19a687ec9fd33d7dfe1820aca","tid":1362250,"uid":119485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:49:05.000Z","msg":"其實好多人都知大部分元朗人都係同暴力事件無關，<br />\n暴力事件只係少數鄉黑問題。<br />\n<br />\n最近有唔少fake news，<br />\n有網民可能因為相信錯誤消息而對某D 無辜市民/商店不滿。<br />\n<br />\n如果元朗村民 / 商店係727 果日<br />\n放置Memo 紙同筆比市民留下祝福字句，<br />\n同時代表自己同鄉黑 黑社會絕無關係，<br />\n遊行人仕經過有Memo 紙地區時亦減少逗留時間同聲量，<br />\n有無得諗？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57058b12c596aae58dbb352917f471beef6777f6","tid":1362250,"uid":3464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T22:51:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借一借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好忘記中環事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【文宣】7.21上環黑警6宗罪懶人包<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361779\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361779</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}